What you expect Lunarpine to admit he got his tail whipped (No pun 
intended)

Lunarpine would be in the tank for a while gettung repaired. his left 
arm was cracked pretty badly, he could feel the technology taking 
hold and making him stronger.

He'd let his gaurd down to fight the sabretooth and let Deathscythe 
practically walk up to him. Every moment in the chamber reminded him 
of that and the only thought going through him was the yearning for 
revenge.

The newcomers seemed to be honoring thier end of the ceasefire or 
another attack would have been launched. The Ark was short handed and 
he was out of battle for a while, the war was looking more bleak by 
the moment.
